CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The stale smell of unwashed clothing and bodies is quite overpowering in this room. From one of the cots near the wall, you can hear the drunken snores of an unfortunate who is down on his luck. The scurrying of rats looking for food can be heard throughout these common sleeping quarters. Only those who can't afford more comfortable digs, and those too besotted from a night in the cantina sleep here.
*DESCRIPTION_END
