NUMBER 212
NAME Rosy's Cantina
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Rosy's Cantina provides its patron with sensory overload. In one corner a band blares out music upon a variety of strange instruments. An assortment of multicolored lights flash across the room, piercing the smoky haze with bright rays. The sounds of laughter, conversation and the occasional challenge, blend with the loud, ecstatic beat of the music. You find your eyes drifting from one mysterious looking person to another, wondering who are the bounty hunters, smugglers and adventurers.
*DESCRIPTION_END
