NUMBER 327
NAME Test Tunnels, Office
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
INDOOR_FLOOR
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
A very small office, more like a cubicle, is here. A single wooden desk sits in the center of the room and a moldy wooden chair is pulled up against the side of the desk. Layers of dust and cobwebs cover both desk and chair, giving them the appearance of being gray in color. Faded and crinkly pictures of naked women cover the walls, their colors so aged that most of the image is undiscernible. Curled up in one dark corner of the room, is a skeleton.
*DESCRIPTION_END
