*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
  Faintly, through the dust you can see some letters engraved into the oaken wood of the desk. After wiping some of the dust away, you can make out the following:

  "They all laughed at old Tuvnie, called him names and pointed at him.
   Now we'll see, now we'll really see, my beautiful little metal creations
   will make them pay for what they did to Tuvnie! Then Tuvnie will laugh!"
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The skeleton is curled up in a pose that makes it look as if it was trying to ward off some attack. Despite a thick layer of dust, one gets the impression that the bones were picked clean, as there is no tissue residue left upon them.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
